Conservation status:― We included this species in the category of vulnerable (VU B2a,b(iii)), according to criterion B, because it has an EOO estimated to be less than 20000 km 2 ( 88.4 km 2 ), the AOO is less than 2000 km 2 ( 16 km 2 ), and it is known from no more than 10 locations (criteria B2a), and grows in a region of continuing habitat reduction (criteria B2b(iii)), as evidenced by several studies in the Colombian eastern cordillera (e.g. Etter and Villa, 2000 ;
Armenteras et al. 2003
